These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, pall-mall, swisher
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, spy, superhero
The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, social-worker, project-manager
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, car, motorbike
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the project-manager##1
2. the engineer is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the montecristo-smoker is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching superhero movies##2
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
5. the project-manager is the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Cigar         | pall-mall | montecristo   | swisher   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | disaster | superhero |
| Job   | project-manager  | engineer    | social-worker      |
| Transport     | car     | bus      | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, raspberry, tomato
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, gospel, soul
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, animation, adventure
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, june, july
1. the fan of soul is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the fan of soul##1
3. the person eating raspberry is the person watching adventure movies##1
4. the person eating kale is the person watching animation movies##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is between the fan of gospel and the person eating tomato##2
6. the person eating tomato is the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Food          | raspberry  | kale     | tomato     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | soul     | blues      |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure  | animation | drama |
| Birthday           | july | january     | june       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, kale, orange
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, photography, filmmaking
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, thriller
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, cricket, handball
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person watching thriller movies##2
3. the person eating eggplant is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is the person eating kale##1
5. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Food          | eggplant  | orange     | kale     |
| Hobby           | filmmaking | gardening  | photography   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | mystery    | thriller |
| Sport           | handball     | biathlon | cricket |

