.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
There 3 different types of food: cherry, cucumber, raspberry
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, french, canadian
3 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, guinea-pig
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, aristoff, bongani
1. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the canadian##1
3. the person eating raspberry is between the french and the owner of the cat##2
4. the person eating cucumber is the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food    | cherry       | raspberry  | cucumber   |
| Nationality     | french    | canadian  | indonesian |
| Pet     | chinchilla   | guinea-pig | cat        |
| Cigar   | bongani | dunhill     | aristoff      |

