The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, october, july
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, funk, gospel
3 different pets are kept: bird, dog, hamster
1. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of funk##1
2. the owner of the bird is between the fan of gospel and the person who's birthday is in july##2
3. the person who's birthday is in march is the owner of the dog##1
4. the blend-smoker is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
5. the owner of the bird is on the left of the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Cigar          | siglo    | blend     | game      |
| Birthday         | march | october | july |
| Music-Genre   | gospel  | funk       | disco       |
| Pet           | dog     | bird       | hamster     |

