.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-6::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, tulip, rose
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, sports, western
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, country, d&b
3 different pets are kept: fish, horse, mouse
1. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
2. the person who growsrose is the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the fan of country is between the person who growstulip and the owner of the horse##2
4. the fan of d&b is on the far right##1
5. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Flower          | tulip | poppy | rose    |
| Movie-Genre         | sports | western      | thriller |
| Music-Genre   | ambient   | country     | d&b        |
| Pet           | fish      | mouse       | horse      |

