The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, fishing, skydiving
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, fantasy, western
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, rowing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who growsamaryllis and the person who's sport is golf##2
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person watching comedy movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Flower          | amaryllis      | orchid   | aconite |
| Hobby         | board-games | fishing | skydiving |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy      | western | fantasy   |
| Sport     | tennis         | rowing  | golf       |

