.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-8::.
3 different games are played: scrabble, domino, backgammon
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, trike, jet-ski
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, dressmaker, journalist
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, gospel, rock
1. the journalist is on the far left##1
2. the person playing domino is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
3. the person playing domino is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
4. the architect is between the person driving the trike and the person playing backgammon##2
5. the person playing domino is the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Game      | scrabble       | domino      | backgammon      |
| Transport         | trike    | jet-ski | roller      |
| Job           | journalist | architect     | dressmaker |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | rock          | folk       |

