.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-9::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, cola
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, vegafina, tiparillo
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, february, august
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, bike, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who's birthday is in august##2
2. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
4. the vegafina-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
6. the person driving the bike is the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | 7up      | almond-milk | cola     |
| Cigar          | vegafina   | dannemann      | tiparillo     |
| Birthday   | august  | january      | february |
| Transport     | airplane | taxi        | bike     |

