The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, project-manager, social-worker
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, lacrosse, sailing
There 3 different types of food: banana, spinach, plum
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
2. the project-manager is between the engineer and the owner of the dog##2
3. the person who's sport is sailing is the owner of the bird##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the social-worker##1
5. the person eating plum is on the left of the engineer##1
6. the person eating banana is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
| Pet       | dog       | bird       | chinchilla    |
| Job         | social-worker | project-manager | engineer |
| Sport       | lacrosse      | sailing         | handball |
| Food   | banana        | plum            | spinach  |

