The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, reading, writing
The people have 3 different jobs:  librarian, chef, photographer
3 different games are played: domino, whist, chess
1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the chef##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person playing chess##1
3. the person playing whist is in the middle##1
4. the person playing whist is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
5. the photographer is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
| Beverage      | milk     | hot-chocolate | coffee      |
| Hobby         | reading  | writing       | board-games |
| Job   | photographer   | chef         | librarian     |
| Game   | domino | whist    | chess     |

