2. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
3. the australian is on the left of the spanish##1
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the owner of the hamster and the person watching musical movies##2
6. the person watching horror movies is the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |       3        |
| Hobby      | fishing | card-games      | board-games            |
| Pet           | snake | hedgehog | hamster |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | sports        | horror         |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | australian    | spanish        |

