3 different pets are kept: snake, turtle, guinea-pig
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, fisherman, police-officer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, disaster, time-travel
1. the malaysian is between the person watching disaster movies and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
2. the malaysian is on the left of the coach##1
3. the police-officer is on the right of the dutch##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the owner of the snake is the person watching disaster movies##1
6. the coach is on the right of the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| Nationality      | dutch    | malaysian          | indian |
| Pet          | guinea-pig | turtle           | snake        |
| Job           | fisherman | police-officer | coach         |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | time-travel    | disaster      |

