.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-15::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, cherry, potato
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, punk, trance
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, mystery, comedy
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, mauve, emerald
1. the fan of trance is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the person who likes mauve is between the fan of trance and the person watching comedy movies##2
3. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far right##1
4. the person eating cherry is between the fan of trance and the person eating artichoke##2
5. the fan of punk is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Food          | potato  | cherry   | artichoke |
| Music-Genre   | trance  | punk     | classical |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | mystery | comedy   |
| Color     | emerald   | mauve   | fuchsia      |

