House: wooden, townhouse, victorian
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, rose, sunflower
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, train, tram
1. the townhouse house is on the right of the person driving the train##1
2. the victorian house is between the person driving the boat and the wooden house##2
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
4. the person who growsrose is the person driving the boat##1
5. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |      3       |
| Hobby       | singing | gardening | magic-tricks |
| House         | wooden   | victorian       | townhouse        |
| Flower       | sunflower | poppy   | rose         |
| Transport   | tram    | train     | boat         |

