The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, skiing, skateboarding
3 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, pony
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, ship, train
1. the person who's sport is skiing is between the person driving the train and the person who's sport is parkour##2
2. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person driving the train##1
3. the person eating grapes is the owner of the dog##1
4. the owner of the pony is the person eating strawberry##1
5. the person driving the airplane is the owner of the hamster##1
6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Food   | grapes | strawberry  | grapefruit     |
| Sport   | skateboarding    | skiing | parkour |
| Pet           | dog        | pony   | hamster  |
| Transport     | train      | ship   | airplane |

