House: colonial, cape-cod, modern
1. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
2. the cape-cod house is on the left of the engineer##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is the colonial house##1
4. the lawyer is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
5. the person watching epic movies is on the far right##1
6. the writer is between the engineer and the person driving the helicopter##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| Job           | lawyer   | writer   | engineer |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | sports   | epic     |
| Transport   | helicopter     | airplane      | bike    |
| House           | colonial | cape-cod | modern    |

