.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, mirinda
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, video-games, woodworking
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, iris, sunflower
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, tennis, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is tennis is the person who growssunflower##1
2. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the person who growsbellflower is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
4. the person who growsiris is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person drinking milk and the person who growsiris##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | mirinda     | milk        |
| Hobby         | video-games   | woodworking | board-games |
| Flower   | iris        | bellflower       | sunflower      |
| Sport           | ice-hockey           | badminton    | tennis       |

