.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, spinach, strawberry
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, mystery, crime
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, snowboarding, surfing
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, january, april
1. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person who's birthday is in june##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person eating strawberry##1
5. the person watching crime movies is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
6. the person who's sport is surfing is the person eating raspberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Food        | spinach      | raspberry | strawberry |
| Movie-Genre         | mystery     | crime    | epic        |
| Sport       | snowboarding | surfing   | lacrosse   |
| Birthday   | june          | january     | april       |

 